A decomposition of the data Ì†µÌ±†(Ì†µÌ±°) into Ì†µÌ±õ-empirical modes is realised by repeating the processure of the nth IMF component Ì†µÌ±êÌ†µÌ±õ until the residue Ì†µÌ±üÌ†µÌ±õ becomes a monotonic function. So the data Ì†µÌ±†(Ì†µÌ±°) can be described as:

